            <div id="collapseG3" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingG3">
              <div class="panel-body">
                <p class="answer">
                  While we cannot guarantee that our estimates are "perfectly" accurate, we try to provide reasonable estimates for our data. For more information, please see the section on "How we get our data".
                </p>
